\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 This project aims to develop a client-server application that enables secure communication among multiple clients connected to a server.\'a0You\'a0have already created an application where a single client can communicate securely. This project extends that by including multiple clients who communicate with each other. The clients will form a group (every client in a single group), and any message or file a client sends will be broadcast to the rest of the group members. The communication will be encrypted using a single key encryption algorithm to ensure confidentiality and security. The application will support text messages and file sharing, with a maximum file size limit of 50 MB.\
