\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Integrity Service: Implement a communication service so that files and messages can be verified to be authentic.\
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Group Chat: Enable clients to join a group (there is only one group that includes all connected clients) and communicate with other group members by sending text messages.\
